# Event Intersection

If events are dependent, we see by the definition of conditional probability that
$$ \bbps{\inflate[]{E}{n}} = \bbps{E_1}\bbps{E_2\;|\;E_1}\ldots\bbps{E_n\;|\;\inflate[]{E}{n-1}}. $$

